data.description: Welcome to your future home! You will find 3 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms providing ample space for comfortable living. The convenience of main floor laundry allow your daily chores to become a breeze. The unfinished basement, already framed, eagerly awaits your finishing touches. Situated in a prime location, close to Highway 70 and 64, ensuring easy access to nearby amenities and a seamless commute. Do not miss the opportunity to make this house your home.
